sql: SELECT Birth_Place FROM people WHERE  Weight = 40 ORDER BY Birth_Place ASC LIMIT 9

SELECT AVG(v.People_ID), COUNT(DISTINCT people.Height), v.Birth_Date FROM people AS v JOIN people ON people.People_ID = v.People_ID WHERE  people.Height > 56 GROUP BY v.Birth_Date HAVING MIN(v.People_ID) > 79 ORDER BY v.Birth_Date ASC

SELECT COUNT(Weight), COUNT(Weight), MIN(Weight), Birth_Place FROM people WHERE  People_ID < 15 OR Weight >= (SELECT AVG(Weight) FROM people AS o WHERE  o.Weight = 10 LIMIT 10) GROUP BY Birth_Place HAVING COUNT(Weight) > 21
SELECT Weight FROM people WHERE  Weight = 98
SELECT Name, Birth_Place FROM people JOIN body_builder ON body_builder.People_ID = people.People_ID LIMIT 3
SELECT SUM(s.Height), MAX(s.Weight), s.Weight FROM people AS s WHERE  s.Weight < 77 GROUP BY s.Weight ORDER BY s.Weight ASC

SELECT SUM(body_builder.Total), COUNT(a.Body_Builder_ID), a.People_ID FROM body_builder AS a JOIN body_builder ON body_builder.Body_Builder_ID = a.Body_Builder_ID WHERE a.Clean_Jerk BETWEEN 1 AND 10 GROUP BY a.People_ID
SELECT Weight FROM people JOIN body_builder ON body_builder.People_ID = people.People_ID WHERE  people.People_ID != 65
SELECT w.People_ID, w.Weight FROM people AS w WHERE w.People_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND  w.People_ID <= 69 GROUP BY w.Weight LIMIT 9
SELECT body_builder.People_ID FROM body_builder AS d JOIN body_builder ON body_builder.Body_Builder_ID = d.Body_Builder_ID WHERE  d.Body_Builder_ID >= 21
SELECT AVG(Height), Name, Name FROM people WHERE  Weight >= 44

SELECT Total, Birth_Place FROM people JOIN body_builder ON body_builder.People_ID = people.People_ID WHERE  Weight < 71 OR Clean_Jerk IN (SELECT Clean_Jerk FROM body_builder WHERE  Snatch = 63) GROUP BY Total HAVING MAX(body_builder.People_ID) >= 45 ORDER BY Total DESC

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT body_builder.Body_Builder_ID), o.Snatch, body_builder.Clean_Jerk FROM body_builder AS o JOIN body_builder ON body_builder.Body_Builder_ID = o.Body_Builder_ID GROUP BY body_builder.Clean_Jerk HAVING AVG(o.Clean_Jerk) < 89

SELECT SUM(Height), COUNT(DISTINCT Total), Weight FROM people JOIN body_builder ON body_builder.People_ID = people.People_ID WHERE People_ID = (SELECT MIN(People_ID) FROM people WHERE  Weight <= 80 LIMIT 2) LIMIT 3
SELECT SUM(j.Weight), j.Birth_Date, j.Height FROM people AS j WHERE  j.People_ID > 63 GROUP BY j.Height HAVING SUM(j.Weight) <= 85
SELECT SUM(z.People_ID), z.Height FROM people AS z WHERE  z.Weight <= 35 GROUP BY z.Height HAVING MIN(z.Height) <= 80 ORDER BY z.Height DESC LIMIT 8
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT Total), Clean_Jerk, Birth_Date FROM people JOIN body_builder ON body_builder.People_ID = people.People_ID WHERE  Total >= 99
SELECT AVG(Height), Weight, Birth_Place FROM people
SELECT Birth_Date FROM people JOIN body_builder ON body_builder.People_ID = people.People_ID WHERE body_builder.People_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 ORDER BY Birth_Date ASC LIMIT 5

SELECT COUNT(body_builder.People_ID), body_builder.Snatch FROM body_builder AS r JOIN body_builder ON body_builder.Body_Builder_ID = r.Body_Builder_ID WHERE  body_builder.Total > 81 GROUP BY body_builder.Snatch HAVING MIN(r.Snatch) <= 86 ORDER BY body_builder.Snatch ASC
SELECT AVG(Height), Weight FROM people JOIN body_builder ON body_builder.People_ID = people.People_ID WHERE  Weight < 63 AND People_ID IN (SELECT People_ID FROM body_builder)
